{"tid":1603794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得返一個方法 可以再有二百萬人或更多","createTime":"2019-09-29T18:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T18:49:10.000Z","uid":259519,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e384fc27f647ed3e0bd9d4c581c4bcd78796004f","tid":1603794,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:39:55.000Z","msg":"一百萬，二百萬，一百七十萬⋯⋯<br />\n之後呢？之後咪就係見到被捕人數不斷上升，香港人贏左啲咩？<span style=\"color: red;\">輸撚曬啦屌你老母</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地輸 係輸在有份工 有糧出！輸在你老母個仔仲要顧撚住自己份工，用手機上網睇TG、食飯對住幾句當支持？？我地唔撚係要依D</span></span><br />\n<br />\n10.1個個都話賀佢老母？你估真係個個放棄得到份工？<br />\n1）朝早時間切斷所有巴士同黨鐵既路線<br />\n2）絕大部份人因交通返唔到工<br />\n3）如果你唔洗返工，仲留係屋企，你<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都係幫兇！死去既義士點撚樣對得住佢地？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我聽過一個故事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有個男仔係街上面跑跑下步，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">見到隻狗</span></span><br />\n一開始佢以為無乜野，但原來隻狗好餓，想食左個男仔。咁隻狗就撲上去咬左幾啖<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">個男仔好痛好痛</span>，一路向後跑，<span style=\"color: blue;\">佢</span>比狗咬到對手流曬血，好痛⋯⋯<br />\n跑左大概20分鐘，途中被狗咬左好多啖，男仔又手無寸鐵還唔到手又怕隻狗啲利牙，係依個時候竟然跑左入一條倔頭路<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">個男仔好驚，好徬徨，淚流滿面。</span>隻狗就兇神惡煞，誓要食到個男仔⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後個男仔活生生咬死左隻狗</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8135c746f3341119867749ed5901151567c55c7f","tid":1603794,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:40:36.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"83022cfe2f54e1bc90756acb826e37ec3019bf1c","tid":1603794,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8135c746f3341119867749ed5901151567c55c7f","tid":1603794,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:40:36.000Z","msg":"收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:42:44.000Z","msg":"你繼續做奴隸啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1acbce7b158b83b6bd29101e8532b7c44064b5","tid":1603794,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8847d1b7be63b7520cf8b013e175d03f3a1d619","tid":1603794,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"101 番乜柒工? 弱智?"},{"pid":"b87c0342f3736e781559562724407e48db5dbb39","tid":1603794,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8847d1b7be63b7520cf8b013e175d03f3a1d619","tid":1603794,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:46:44.000Z","msg":"101 番乜柒工? 弱智?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T18:49:10.000Z","msg":"大撚把唔撚係放銀行假既人仲去返工 姑勿論最後佢地返唔返到工 佢地係去返工&gt;光復香港"}]}